fld_6282664.caption: Select this option if you would like to affiliate with the Eastern Section of SSA. For more information on the Eastern Section, please visit: www.seismosoc.org/inside-eastern-section/

fld_346590.label: Eastern Section (Two-Year)
fld_346590.caption: Select this option if you would like to affiliate with the Eastern Section of SSA. For more information on the Eastern Section, please visit: www.seismosoc.org/inside-eastern-section/

fld_1967448.label: EERI Affiliation (One-Year)
fld_1967448.caption: Please select this option if you would like to affiliate with the Earthquake Engineering Research Institute (EERI). Those that affiliate with EERI will receive EERI's bi-weekly e-newsletter, semi-annual magazine publication, and special member rates for EERI meetings, conferences, publications, and audio-visual materials. Affiliates will be included in and have access to the EERI membership roster. Those members of SSA seeking full benefits of an EERI membership, including access to Earthquake Spectra, should not opt to become an affiliate and instead should join EERI as a regular member. For more information on EERI and becoming a regular member, please visit www.EERI.org.

fld_1737292.label: EERI Affiliation (Two-Year)
fld_1737292.caption: Please select this option if you would like to affiliate with the Earthquake Engineering Research Institute (EERI). Those that affiliate with EERI will receive EERI's bi-weekly e-newsletter, semi-annual magazine publication, and special member rates for EERI meetings, conferences, publications, and audio-visual materials. Affiliates will be included in and have access to the EERI membership roster. Those members of SSA seeking full benefits of an EERI membership, including access to Earthquake Spectra, should not opt to become an affiliate and instead should join EERI as a regular member. For more information on EERI and becoming a regular member, please visit www.EERI.org.

config.default: Contribute to the Seismological Society of America

fld_3437159.label: Student Travel Grant Fund
fld_3437159.caption: Support students with travel grants to attend the SSA Annual Meeting.

fld_4839579.label: Kanamori Fund
fld_4839579.caption: Provide professional development opportunities for students and seismologists of all ages and support SSA's ability to move quickly in pursuit of new program ideas on behalf of the community. Named in honor of Hiroo Kanamori, the Kanamori Fund has made possible special workshops and helped support travel grants to SSA meetings from countries that are members of the European Seismological Commission.

fld_9165499.label: General Fund
fld_9165499.caption: Support new and ongoing programs in publishing, meetings and communications. Help SSA broaden the reach of the scientific content published in SSA's journals and delivered at its annual meeting. Your contributions to the SSA General Fund make it possible to explore new ways to serve the community.

fld_1563169.label: Geosciences Congressional Visits Day Fund
fld_1563169.caption: Support student participation in Geosciences Congressional Visits Day, held annually to raise awareness about the geosciences among policymakers. Decision-makers need to hear from geoscientists, and students need to learn how to advocate on behalf of our community. Help make this possible with your donation.

fld_736280.label: Joyner Fund
fld_736280.caption: Donate to the William B. Joyner Memorial Fund, which supports a lecture series that fosters the exchange of information at the interface of earthquake science and earthquake engineering.

fld_7183177.label: Affiliated Institution
fld_7183177.caption: Begin typing the name of your institution to locate it within the database. If your institution name does not appear, please type the full institution name to add it to our database.
